The painting is thought to be the work of an unidentified Netherlandic artist. Nor is it known who composed the poem.l Stranger, perhaps, is the fact that nowhere on this monumenta! epitaph does the name of the deceased occur. The church is full of epitaphs of various members of the Rosenkrantz family, all duly named.
